#TBT to last year’s Ferrari Racing Days where more than 100 Ferraris raced around Road Atlanta.⁣
⁣
Tomorrow, #FerrariRacingDays is back, this time at the renowned Indianapolis Motor Speedway. Prepare for an even more spectacular event with just as many Ferraris in attendance, but with the special addition of the iconic Ferrari Monza models.⁣
⁣
Tune in to live.ferrari.com to follow the action.⁣
⁣
#Ferrari #Motorsports #FerrariChallenge

A day to remember for #Ferrari fans: July 8, 1990. Alain Prost conquers the 100th win of @scuderiaferrari in Formula 1 at the Circuit Paul Ricard.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
80 adrenaline-filled laps on board the #FerrariF190 to reach that goal. This legendary Formula 1 Racing Car, also known as the Ferrari 641, is now on display at the MoMA as part of the new “Automania” exhibit.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
#Formula1 #MoMA #Automania @themuseumofmodernart
